    </li>
    <li>
    <p><strong>Session cookies and preference cookies</strong></p>
    These cookies allow you to enter the protected sections of our website, add products to the shopping cart or use the electronic payment system. Such cookies expire at the end of the session of the visit. We may also use cookies that last longer and are created in order to remember your preferences and choices during your visit to our site. The life cycle of such cookies does not exceed one year.</p>
